{"tid":1038042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共推「魯班工坊」宣傳科技實力","createTime":"2019-02-26T11:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T19:40:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"81448f020f9fa8b6d4bd3b53dfb37e7879b713b2","tid":1038042,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T11:32:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190226/20620754\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190226%2F20620754&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6ceYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=739179d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190226%2F20620754&h=b4af7953\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190226/20620754</a><br />\n<br />\n中共推「魯班工坊」宣傳科技實力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190226/large/a1404a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190226%2Flarge%2Fa1404a.gif&h=fff5e457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泰國學生參加魯班工坊。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n中共在海外搞孔子學院，被多國封殺，現在決定大力推動「魯班工坊」，宣傳中國「中國製造2025」等科技實力，泰國是最新一個同意合作與建魯班工坊的國家。<br />\n<br />\n官方指，「魯班工坊」是「把優秀職業教育成果輸出國門與世界分享的重要平台」。換言之即是「孔子學院」的科技版，用作宣傳「中國製造2025」的機構。自2018年開始，該專案已經延伸到泰國、印度、英國、印尼、巴基斯坦、柬埔寨和葡萄牙等7個國家，共涉及自動化、新能源、機械、汽車、鐵道、通訊、電子資訊、餐飲等8類19個專業，分中等職業學校、高等職業院校及本科院校。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多國抵制關閉孔子學院<br />\n<br />\n《新華社》在23日刊登中國國務院印發的文件「加快推進教育現代化實施方案（2018-2022年）」，當中重點任務是「推進共建一帶一路教育行動」，裏面便強調「要鼓勵有條件的職業院校在海外建設魯班工坊」，泰國是最新建設魯班工坊的國家，機構在去年年底正式揭牌。在文件推出後，相信中國將更積極推動魯班工坊。<br />\n<br />\n西方國家一直對孔子學院及魯班工坊存有極大戒心，斥之為收集海外情報的機構，近年美國、法國、瑞典、加拿大等多所大學抵制並關閉孔子學院，認為學院具有政治目的，干涉學術自由。<br />\n<br />\n《自由時報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n美籲棄華為5G改用諾基亞愛立信<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n柯文哲訪以 批台兵役浪費時間"},{"pid":"a16165d703b20573cb73af9e053c870d7b998726","tid":1038042,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T11:43:42.000Z","msg":"中国的..."},{"pid":"394a7352a092bae8fc005efb05473b911f3a395e","tid":1038042,"uid":70977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T11:47:54.000Z","msg":"我諗如果佢係教傳統木工技藝應該好多人搶住學 <br />\n但如果係教圖個啲就中國的會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb5c7ce19220f82bc8dfba46bec4d4313f97177","tid":1038042,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:36:19.000Z","msg":"推廣支那老婆秘錄好過喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609782aa0ae862d910c44ec62a0ea3fecdeadde7","tid":1038042,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗如果佢係教<span style=\"color: red;\">傳統木工技藝</span>應該好多人搶住學 <br />\n但如果係教圖個啲就中國的會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要學都向架仔學喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8b294dd3cd70d20a5c08c1c1dbe067aa4b0039","tid":1038042,"uid":162535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609782aa0ae862d910c44ec62a0ea3fecdeadde7","tid":1038042,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗如果佢係教<span style=\"color: red;\">傳統木工技藝</span>應該好多人搶住學 <br />\n但如果係教圖個啲就中國的會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />